": "redpillbot", "username": "redpillb0t"}, "content": "Bill Gates: \u201cCows make 6% of global emissions.\u201d\n\n\u201cYou can either fix the cows, or make beef without the cow.\u201d\n\nThat\u2019s the conversation now: not about farming, not about land use \u2014 but redesigning the cow itself.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 3351}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2050663670812729758", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZfAQEVB", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 73, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8596795, "raw_content": "", "author": "rdvs34283", "created": 1777813498334, "profile_picture": "p9HQtdiLq2uP", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Blue_Falcons_Suck", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZfAQEVB.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/wallstreetmav/status/2050663670812729758", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Gee, I wonder what happened.", "last_comment_created": 1777830890867, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 7, "score_up": 73, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": [{"width": 896, "heightRatio": 93, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HHVrfEeWQAAENfY.jpg", "height": 834}], "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 167, "created": 1777751293000, "id": "2050663670812729758", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1482179968083836928/7prxRZ4M_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Wall Street Mav", "username": "WallStreetMav"}, "content": "South Africa used to be way ahead of other African countries and strongly above the average for emerging economies.\n\nBut something happened the past 20 years, they are falling behind \u2026 now they have electricity blackouts, public infrastructure is falling apart.\n\nWhat changed?", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 609}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZfBXFmE", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 21, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8597292, "raw_content": "I'm not alone in schadenfreude on the leftists with the SCOTUS decision on Louisiana vs. Callais; however, an observation:  This decision has created a LOT more caterwauling in all leftists, dems, influencers, and bots in all of the social media venues, not seen since Trump's 2nd win.\n\nLooking past the usual BS virtue signaling and ongoing conditioning to keep their base big mad, I believe that this is a huge indicator of dread at their party's future prospect of winning, and that is a damn good thing.", "author": "EricCIAmiredFella2", "created": 1777837867048, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "EricCIAmiredFella2", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "SCOTUS and rustled jimmies", "last_comment_created": 1777839924744, "content": "<p>I'm not alone in schadenfreude on the leftists with the SCOTUS decision on Louisiana vs. Callais; however, an observation:  This decision has created a LOT more caterwauling in all leftists, dems, influencers, and bots in all of the social media venues, not seen since Trump's 2nd win.</p>\n<p>Looking past the usual BS vir